summary: Adds a new NPC, Cornelius, to the front of the College of Winterhold. You can find him in the front, waiting for someone to help him with a problem.
descriptionHtml:
UPDATE v1.2
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________
- This update should (hopefully) fix the audio problems alot of people have been having, if not please inform me!
- Thanks to FoulCreature for helping me alot with fixing this problem! :D  (if it works, if it doesn\'t entirely my fault :p)
-Look forward to the first content update which will add a new quest expanding this storyline hopefully this week or early next!
_________________________________________________________________________________________
INSTALL
-Extract the files in the .rar into your Skyrim/Data folder. Make sure to activate the .esp in your Skyrim launcher, found in Data Files.
_________________________________________________________________________________________

This is my very first mod, I hope you enjoy :)

Adds a new NPC, Cornelius II, to the front of the College of Winterhold. You can find him in front of the statue in the middle of the college, waiting for someone to help him with a problem. 

-Character is voiced almost fully by my brother, Jordan Eli
-Earn a reward for completing his quest

Currently working on 1st content update, stay tuned! :D

IMPORTANT INFORMATION! PLEASE READ!!

Do not download if you are currenlty in the Midden and plan on returning to the surface after you complete the College of Winterhold\'s quest you are currently on because you will encounter a vital part of my quest and might break it. Thank you.

Please rate and give feedback!
author: Vampet6
